title: Zoe Gagalis
text: Thank you for visiting my website! My name is Zoe, I am a current senior at Colorado State University, studying ecosystem science and sustainability. I will be graduating in May 2025 and I am looking for work in corporate sustainability and conservation. Please browse my recent projects as well as my resume, Linkedin, and contact information.
